  "1679290": {
    "name": "Fire & Maneuver",
    "steam_appid": 1679290,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679290/extras/161d2fcdc5ed9bfc4d65389c1ca84b55.webp?t=1770062084\" width=600 height=48 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >概述</h2>来自The Armchair History团队的《火力与策略》是一款独特的战略游戏，由历史爱好者为历史爱好者、战争游戏爱好者和休闲玩家共同打造。通过深入的历史研究，F&amp;M将栩栩如生的战斗单位与充满激情的团队开发的巧妙而引人入胜的游戏机制相结合，打造了一款集历史和可玩性于一体的战略游戏，让每个人都能找到乐趣。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679290/extras/0a660433556beff91414c638df480c45.poster.avif?t=1770062084\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679290/extras/0a660433556beff91414c638df480c45.webm?t=1770062084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679290/extras/0a660433556beff91414c638df480c45.mp4?t=1770062084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>沉浸在维多利亚时代的战争中，每时每刻都似乎带来新的战术或技术创新。在F&amp;M中，您的唯一目标是军事胜利，忘记政治和经济事务。与朋友们在历史战役的再现中较量，或者为欧洲开辟一条新路。在进攻和守势之间谨慎权衡，因为持续进攻会消耗宝贵资源。随着新国家和单位的不断开发，发现在历史篇章上留下自己名字的新方法。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679290/extras/ae56e27f411574e7bcdaee60b043240a.webp?t=1770062084\" width=600 height=35 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679290/extras/bdb52ac2a41f89b4d3397e25685b3f5f.poster.avif?t=1770062084\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679290/extras/bdb52ac2a41f89b4d3397e25685b3f5f.webm?t=1770062084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679290/extras/bdb52ac2a41f89b4d3397e25685b3f5f.mp4?t=1770062084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >独特的回合制战斗</h2>没有计划能在与敌人的第一次接触中生存，F&amp;M让您身处历史上的将军，预测对手的行动。<br><br><br>游戏创新的“同时回合制”要求您仔细考虑对手可能采取的行动。不是被动等待对已经发生的行动做出反应，而是要积极考虑所有可能性，决定对手最可能采取哪种战术选择……以及您能接受不回应哪种选择。撤退到更有利的地形，积极进攻，或者干脆扎根观察对手的行动——选择权在您手中，您的命令是最终的。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679290/extras/ae56e27f411574e7bcdaee60b043240a.webp?t=1770062084\" width=600 height=35 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战役模式</h2>玩四个独特的战役，包括法普战争、克里米亚战争、奥普战争和高加索战场。每个战役都可以从任何角度进行游戏，并可以 与朋友一起在多人游戏中进行战斗！使用全新的团队技能树自定义您的师团并个性化您的部队。独特的历史事件系统以及军事学说系统使每次战役的游戏体验都完全独特。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679290/extras/8ff31a81e9e6f85fbee46f343837d0ea.poster.avif?t=1770062084\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679290/extras/8ff31a81e9e6f85fbee46f343837d0ea.webm?t=1770062084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679290/extras/8ff31a81e9e6f85fbee46f343837d0ea.mp4?t=1770062084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>新的线性场景系统也首次亮相，让您可以在一系列历史战役中进行战斗，重现著名的千人远征等战役。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679290/extras/ae56e27f411574e7bcdaee60b043240a.webp?t=1770062084\" width=600 height=35 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多人游戏</h2>与朋友们进行战斗，或与其他执政者展开较量，您可以在预设的历史场景中扮演莫尔特克或巴赞，也可以进行完全的历史幻想，让英国红衣军队与德国克虎门炮在俄罗斯草原上交锋。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679290/extras/38cc60c07fdf43c8e9c5bd8db8042380.poster.avif?t=1770062084\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679290/extras/38cc60c07fdf43c8e9c5bd8db8042380.webm?t=1770062084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679290/extras/38cc60c07fdf43c8e9c5bd8db8042380.mp4?t=1770062084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>F&amp;M旨在奖励优秀的统帅才能而非偶然的运气。在击败其他玩家时，自豪地佩戴胜利的荣誉，确信您真正赢得了每场胜利。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679290/extras/ae56e27f411574e7bcdaee60b043240a.webp?t=1770062084\" width=600 height=35 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1853-1871 年的势力</h2>统领欧洲及其他地区最强大的军队，欣赏您的部队在游戏的早期和晚期取得的发展。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679290/extras/40535165c1ffb52c55a91e9e79393e5a.poster.avif?t=1770062084\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679290/extras/40535165c1ffb52c55a91e9e79393e5a.webm?t=1770062084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679290/extras/40535165c1ffb52c55a91e9e79393e5a.mp4?t=1770062084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679290/extras/55042055f47465d85a2a77fc3b4772cd.webp?t=1770062084\" width=12 height=12 /></span> <strong>法兰西第二帝国</strong><br>拥有平衡而多样的部队，包括非常耐用的外籍军团……但要小心敌人数量和火炮质量的优势。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679290/extras/809c7eb644fadaa34494c9656ea8d199.webp?t=1770062084\" width=12 height=12 /></span> <strong>北德联邦</strong><br>曾经是普鲁士王国，这个新国家拥有强大的指挥官，他们领导着来自整个德意志诸国的武装部队，从巴伐利亚和符腾堡步兵到令人恐惧的克虎门火炮……但要注意您快速射击步枪的短射程以及这给您的士兵带来的危险。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679290/extras/980965a6492374b61bd5c87a5c13c4ca.webp?t=1770062084\" width=12 height=12 /></span> <strong>大英帝国</strong><br>严格训练的步兵发射惩罚性的齐射，著名的苏格兰高地步兵可以击退任何冲向他们阵线的敌人……但要小心您部队的高昂成本，这在游戏中是最高的。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679290/extras/c6263a3cfaf33b76919d01c4699a37ea.webp?t=1770062084\" width=12 height=12 /></span> <strong>俄罗斯帝国</strong><br>依靠数量优势和士兵的狂热将敌人从战场上扫荡出去，用进攻性的步兵纵队支援，同时让令人畏惧的哥萨克骑兵绕到敌人后方……但要注意在战斗中失去对士兵的控制。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679290/extras/fe4c07ee28dbb58e7b71e5cc08a12f45.webp?t=1770062084\" width=12 height=12 /></span> <strong>奥斯曼帝国</strong><br>用看似无穷无尽的民兵潮涌向战场，包括西方人称为“疯狂头颅”的奇特“巴什巴祖克”……但要小心奥斯曼军队普遍存在的缺乏纪律。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679290/extras/fef3de896f3058a3352e26f3a97c1620.webp?t=1770062084\" width=12 height=12 /></span> <strong>奥地利帝国</strong><br>在一个军队中找到两种力量的平衡，包括擅长远程作战的专家侦查兵……但要注意这个独特优势在战斗越来越激烈时变成劣势。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679290/extras/1fabccc00fae02f2596937718a2283b1.webp?t=1770062084\" width=12 height=12 /></span> <strong>意大利王国</strong><br>民族主义使您能够动用山地部队和政治准军事力量……但要注意您的特种部队缺乏专业素质。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679290/extras/03bafdd4378fb811594888b3aa389e45.webp?t=1770062084\" width=600 height=48 /></span>",
